Package: Odyssey
Title: Interactive Data Discovery Tool for Exploring Biodiversity Data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Nikos", "Pechlivanis", , "nikosp41@certh.gr", role = "cre"),
    person("Natasa", "Anastasiadou", , "nanastasiadou@certh.gr", role = "aut")
     )
Description: Odyssey is an interactive Shiny application designed as a data discovery tool 
             for exploring biodiversity.It provides dynamic visualizations, 
             interactive tables, and geospatial representations to help users
             navigate and interpret molecular biodiversity data.
